I was definitely disappointed by the International Texting Service (which Fongo charges for). Fongo has problems with certain SMS short messages texting services. For example it will not work with Lyft and I believe the same is true for Uber. Since I use these services in the US I need access to the SMS short message service for account verification.  I only found this out after I purchased the package which is too late and can only be described as disappointing (to be polite).  To summarize Fongo is selling a PARTIAL texting service and not a complete texting service. My advice is to stay away until the SMS problem is fixed and a complete package is available.
